                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since they uses SparkContext?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12981184">SPARK-16088</key>
            <summary>Update setJobGroup, clearJobGroup, cancelJobGroup SparkR API to not require sc</summary>
